reinterpreted Perfume of History François Rancé dedicated this perfume to the woman Napoleon loved most. The intensity of Spring flowers, the joyful, sensuous, exotic notes, and the penetrating and lavish combination of fruits and wood create a fresh harmonious flowery fragrance conducive to sensuousness in an atmosphere rich in elegance.
